<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Services</title>
    <style>
      
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-right: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), -5px -5px 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        main {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
            animation: floatText 3s ease infinite alternate;
        }

           @keyframes floatText {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        .service-card {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), -10px -10px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .service-card h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .service-card p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li class="<%= active === 'home' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li class="<%= active === 'about' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li class="<%= active === 'projects' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a href="/projects">Projects</a></li>
                <li class="<%= active === 'services' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
                <li class="<%= active === 'contact' ? 'active' : '' %>"><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <h1>Services</h1>
        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Clean Code</h2>
            <p>Specialized in writing clean and well-organized code. Also best practices and standards to ensure the highest quality code for your projects.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Great Support</h2>
            <p>I provide exceptional support to the clients, ensuring a smooth and hassle-free experience. Also available to assist you with any questions or concerns.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
